description: Number of partitions of n into parts 6k+4 or 6k+5.
formula: a(n) ~ exp(Pi*sqrt(2*n)/3) * Gamma(2/3) * Gamma(5/6) / (4 * sqrt(3*Pi) * n). - _Vaclav Kotesovec_, Aug 27 2015
mathematica: nmax = 100; Rest[CoefficientList[Series[Product[1/((1 - x^(6k+4))*(1 - x^(6k+5))), {k, 0, nmax}], {x, 0, nmax}], x]] (* _Vaclav Kotesovec_, Aug 27 2015 *)
